
       void ttv_DisplayActivateSimulation(char mode);

DDEESSCCRRIIPPTTIIOONN
       Enables  the  construction  and simulation of the spice deck of a given
       path, when a reporting request occurs for  this  path.  The  simulation
       columns  in  the report appear automatically except explicitly disabled
       with _t_t_v___D_i_s_p_l_a_y_P_a_t_h_D_e_t_a_i_l_H_i_d_e_C_o_l_u_m_n.

AARRGGUUMMEENNTTSS
       mmooddee          _y_e_s or _n_o to activate or deactivate spice deck  construc-
                     tion and simulation

